<section id="statement">
<div class="container" id="rideco"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2"><p class="lead">“TheRideCo?”  What is TheRideCo you might be asking your self?  It’s what ever you want it to be that includes cycling.  Riding on your own, with a group, gear, bikes, clothing, trails, trail building, and advocacy.  TheRideCo isn’t about one group of cyclists, it’s about all cycling company.</p></div></div></div>
</section>

<section id="brands" name="brands" style="background-color:#fff;">
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">

      <div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
  <!-- Indicators -->
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <% @brands.each_with_index do |brand, index| %>
            <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="<%= index %>" class="<% if index == 0 %>active<% end %>"></li>
          <% end %>
        </ol>

        <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
        <div class="carousel-inner" style="min-height:550px;border:10px solid rgba(0,0,0,.1);">
          <% @brands.each_with_index do |brand, index| %>
            <div class="item <% if index == 0 %>active<% end %>" style="min-height:550px;background:url('<%= brand.main_image.url %>') 50% 125px no-repeat;">
              <%#= image_fu brand.logo_image, "120x120#c" %>

              <div class="row" style="padding:30px 0 30px 0;">
                <div class="col-md-3 col-md-offset-2">
                  <%= image_tag brand.logo_image.url, class: 'img-responsive' %>
                  <%#= image_tag brand.main_image.url %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6" style="background-color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);">
                  <h1><%= brand.name %></h1>
                  <%= raw brand.intro_text %>
                </div>

              </div>



              

              
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

        <!-- Controls -->
          <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
          </a>
          <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
          </a>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>


<section id="trail-advocacy" name="trail-advocacy" data-speed="4" data-type="background">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <h1>Bike and Trail Advocacy</h1>
        <p class="lead">Building communities that support and cultivate cycling.</p>
        <p>Over 14 years of experience planning and building trails, training and advising trail builders and communities, and planning and coordinating cycling and trail events.</p>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <ul>
          <li>Certified Trail Master via http://www.traildesign.com</li>
          <li>COO of human powered trails from 2000 to 2008.  Responsible for, planing, design, volunteer recruitmentli implementation.</p>
          <li>Design/buils on several IMBA courses from pump track to Fat Bikes</li>
        </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <ul>
          <li>Closely involved with KORC from 2011-present.  Trail design and implementation. Active in trail design and building for all seasons.</li>
<li>Race director for La Crosse Criterium and TT 2010, 2011, 2012. </li> 
<li>Race director for the MNMBS Border Battle 2012, 2013, 2014.  Voted Race of the Year in 2013.</li>
</ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


